snippet.title: July Monthly -Erin Condren - New Teacher Oh So Retro 2020-2021 - Moving In (used as Life Planner)
snippet.description:
July Monthly -Erin Condren - New Teacher Oh So Retro 2020-2021 - Moving In (used as Life Planner)

Hi Everybody!!

~~Welcome to my Channel~~
Thank you for watching.  Please SUBSCRIBE to my channel, so you can see what else I'm up too.
If you like the video, please give it a 👍

July monthly - Erin Condren - Plan With Me - In 2020-2021 Oh So Retro NEW Teacher planner.  Looking forward to filling it out with you in future videos.   With new stickers and lots ideas. I know this video launch is WAY in advance, again.  However, I am just so excited to start moving into planner.   Especially due to the timing with pandemic.  

Little more about me: 6th video.  Looking forward to planning with you, in the upcoming videos. No new items this week for producing these videos - hopefully next week.  I have launched more planner stickers to Etsy shop.  Check them out;-)

***Our Etsy shop IS up and running.   Over the next week or so there will be a wider selection of stickers.  NAME:   StickingwithUS

~~~Music by:
www.bensound.com
Royalty Free Music from Bensound

~~~Apple Pro & Pen 
Pro: Apple Pro 12.9" 
Pen: Gen 2 

~~~Lighting
Emart 600W Photography Photo Video Portrait Studio  

Favorite pens!!  
Frixon Clicker Erasable pens - Seriously the best.   Someone made a comment some time ago on a facebook group and in love ever since. 

Business Inquiries: stickingwithus247@gmail.com

Talk to you soon ;-)
Fawne 

Thanks for watching
